---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
import Newsletter from "../components/Newsletter.astro";
---
<Base
  title="About DogGuideHub"
  description="Learn about DogGuideHub's mission to provide trusted, vet-reviewed dog care guidance."
>
  <section class="section about-page">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>About DogGuideHub</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        DogGuideHub was created to give dog owners clear, trustworthy answers — without the guesswork.
      </p>

      <h2>Our Mission</h2>
      <p>
        Raising a dog comes with constant questions: what to feed them, how to spot health problems
        early, which breed fits your lifestyle, and how to protect them financially. We sift through
        research, veterinary guidance, and real owner experience to give you straightforward,
        actionable answers.
      </p>

      <h2>How We Create Our Content</h2>
      <p>
        Every guide on DogGuideHub is researched with accuracy and practicality in mind. We reference
        veterinary sources, industry data, and product comparisons to help you make informed decisions
        for your dog — whether that's choosing a food brand, understanding a symptom, or comparing
        insurance plans.
      </p>

      <h2>How We Support This Site</h2>
      <p>
        DogGuideHub is reader-supported. Some links on this Site are affiliate links, meaning we may
        earn a commission if you make a purchase or sign up through them, at no extra cost to you. This
        allows us to keep producing free content for dog owners. Learn more in our
        <a href="/affiliate-disclosure">Affiliate Disclosure</a>.
      </p>

      <h2>Get In Touch</h2>
      <p>
        Have a question, suggestion, or correction? We'd love to hear from you at
        <a href="mailto:contact@dogguidehub.com">contact@dogguidehub.com</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Newsletter />
</Base>

<style>
  .about-page {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 48px 20px;
  }
  .about-page h1 { color: var(--primary-dark); }
  .about-page h2 { margin-top: 32px; color: var(--primary-dark); font-size: 20px; }
  .about-page p { color: var(--text-muted); }
  .about-page a { color: var(--primary); font-weight: 600; }
  .lead { font-size: 18px; color: var(--text); }
</style>